strings: <voice_0x010011A4><se_def>rice: You know, I wasn't expecting this to happen until we met him.
<voice_0x010011A5><se_def>rice: Do we both carry on with my father's work? Who can tell
<voice_0x010011A6><se_def>rice: Looking back, I can't believe how jealous we were that we had different heirs.
<voice_0x010011A7><se_def>rice: It's incredible how people can change over time.
<voice_0x010011AA><se_def>rice: Don't worry. I'm not suggesting anything. Let's go. It's going to rain!
<voice_0x010011AB><se_high>breathe!: I swear to Casey. My family is going traveling.
<voice_0x010011AD><se_high>breathe!: Now that we work together, the Golding family can thrive more than ever. Compliance!
